    "description": "Condition number and matrix stability"
  },
  "rule-linear-independence": {
    "prefix": "rule-linear-independent",
    "body": [
      "# Vectors are linearly independent if:",
      "# The only solution to c₁v₁ + c₂v₂ + ... + cₙvₙ = 0 is c₁=c₂=...=cₙ=0",
      "# For matrix A with columns v₁, v₂, ..., vₙ:",
      "# - rank(A) = n ⟺ columns are linearly independent",
      "# - det(A) ≠ 0 ⟺ columns are linearly independent (square matrix)",
